{"tid":58212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友好似帽左 應該點安慰佢","createTime":"2016-12-28T15:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T15:46:08.000Z","uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"037b1aa6313cc356ac46b094085ddd11d46ad31c","tid":58212,"uid":4510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友同佢女朋友之前一齊左成兩年 但因為某d原因分開左 但最近復合左兩個月到<br />\n但復合之後 平時佢女朋友就成日同個男仔Skype 最過份試過連續差唔多成40個鐘<br />\n但係佢仲覺得無事 我朋友仲繼續包容距<br />\n<br />\n到左今日<br />\n佢女朋友今日襯我朋友飲醉酒唔知 就約果個男仔出街 同埋送禮物比個男仔 但係我朋友連條毛都收唔到<br />\n依家我朋友好頹 應該點安慰佢好 佢又應該點做好<br />\n<br />\n利申：我的朋友真的不是我"},{"pid":"67a506ebd4022a6453bfecad12c5d4e5ec38bf66","tid":58212,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"多個兄弟姐"},{"pid":"62885a42c5f7eca1fb12424295716aeb22935bcc","tid":58212,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2fa153e43afe7658381cbcbaeb02e57b54764f","tid":58212,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"互射<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fe91bf00244d5ff9279f04a052cb7ceb92ebc5","tid":58212,"uid":5479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"頂帽咪禮物囉點會毛都冇"},{"pid":"4d277ff9f842c5bafc1f95e9d9fbbfeedb688b03","tid":58212,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcGHwKV4XarXN2X9uyyPtsqxWgsRAVYddkc1L1519FYDi?filename=z0GRx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0GRx.gif&h=d0612ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}